Class CharacterStateRow

java.lang.Object
  edu.upenn.cis.ppod.model.PersistentObject
      edu.upenn.cis.ppod.model.PPodEntity
          edu.upenn.cis.ppod.model.CharacterStateRow
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAttachee, IPersistentObject, IPPodVersioned
public final class CharacterStateRow
extends PPodEntity

Rows of a CharacterStateMatrix.

In Hibernate, composite elements may contain components but not collections - that's why this is an entity and not a component class: it needs to contain a List<CharacterStateCell>.

Author:
Sam Donnelly
